    "(2) You have just created a profile.",
    "In setting it up, you have consented to sharing information about you to third parties.",
    "You have added a profile picture, a brief description of yourself, and have engaged on the platform by 'liking' or 'following' other posts and accounts.",
    "You have further made your views known by writing public tweets.",
    "An artificially intelligent poll could scrape your page and extract sociodemographic, geographic and behavioural cues to create a profile about you."
